The subroutines can be tested with

prompt$  gfortran test_grid_interp.f90 splift.f90  splint.f90  spliq.f90

where you can change gfortran for any other fortran compiler.

See test_grid_interp.f90 for an example on how to use those subroutines

Early description of the original subroutines:

https://www.osti.gov/servlets/purl/1545814

The present subroutines are compatible with the original.
